{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban textual based large audience social media platforms",
        "additional_details": "These platforms allow unlimited followers and following and do not require a verified photo of the user to use the application.\r\nWe think that they allow hate speech and defamatory content to spread virally.\r\nThey are the free to use platforms. We think they allow the spread of hate speech, and allow the incitement of violence and anti social behaviour, giving victims life long horrific memories.",
        "background": "Textual based social media platforms need to be banned immediately until content regulation is voted in. A digital health and safety board must be setup to pass these apps.",
